To build the mobl manual you need:

* Calibre: http://calibre-ebook.com/ with command-line tools enabled (Settings > Advanced > Enable command line interface)
* HTMLDoc: http://www.htmldoc.org/ for mac: port install htmldoc
* ronn: http://rtomayko.github.com/ronn/ or: gem install ronn

Then simply type `make clean && make`
